'''
Do reweighting using COLVAR files 
'''
dist1, dist2, cn, fes, Nbins_D1, Nbins_D2, Nbins_CN, Bonds_D1, Bonds_D2, Bonds_CN = [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)], [None for _ in range(Nsystems)]
for i in range(Nsystems):    
    dist1[i], dist2[i], cn[i], fes[i], Nbins_D1[i], Nbins_D2[i], Nbins_CN[i], Bonds_D1[i], Bonds_D2[i], Bonds_CN[i] = read_fes_3d(FOLDERS[i], NAME = '80')
    reweight_3d(COLVARS[i], 
                dist1[i], dist2[i], cn[i], fes[i], 
                Nbins_D1[i], Nbins_D2[i], Nbins_CN[i], Bonds_D1[i], Bonds_D2[i], Bonds_CN[i],
                FOLDERS[i]
                )

In[11]:
def darien_color(color, factor=0.5):
    rgb = matplotlib.colors.to_rgb(color)
    return tuple(max(0, x * factor) for x in rgb)

def format_labels(x, pos):
    if x < 1:
        return f'{x:.1f}'
    else: 
        return x

    display(df)

    plt.errorbar(len(COLVARS[i])/df['N_blocks']/(1000**2), df['dG1_mean'], df['dG1_std'], fmt='.-',

                #marieredgecolor = 'i',
                label = f'{SYS_NAME}, D489'
                )

                color = darien_color(colors[SYS_NAME]),
                capsize=3,
